  <p>
   <font color="#800000">
    <font size="+1">
     Academics
    </font>
   </font>
   My research interests are computer-aided verification and control
of reactive, real-time, hybrid, and probabilistic systems, software verification and
programming languages,
logic, and automata theory.
  </p>
